summary: Adds trees to whiterun, as well as some other small details.
descriptionHtml:
Just to answer some FAQs.

-Yes, the trees can be seen from the outside.

-Yes, you might have FPS drops depending on your setup considering a lot of new shadows have to be rendered.

-I currently have plans for Riften and will probably be the next \"project\". It won\'t be *just* trees.

-Has been updated 4 times, fixed some trees and added some more shrub to hide trees just popping out of the ground, added several rocks and details around the market well.


Also the link for the workshop, just in case.
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=9645

Hope you\'ll be satisfied :)



Lite version is up! My pc had no fps problems in whiterun with this one, and it\'s pretty medium. I hope it\'s what you\'ve wanted. Tried my best to make it also look beautiful.
Thanks to chrisdragon425 for suggesting the lite version.
author: PixelRabbit
